localization.ja: エックスダイステーク

description.en: STAKE is a new ERC20-type (implemented as an ERC677) token designed to secure the on-chain payment layer and provide a mechanism for validators to receive multiple POS incentives. It is an ERC20-based staking token with a market driven value.
